<div id="intro">
  <p>Tomatoes is a <i>pomodoro tracker</i>, a Pomodoro technique® driven time tracker.</p>
  <p>Use the Pomodoro technique® to track your working time in 25-minutes slot called <i>pomodoro</i>.</p>
</div>

<div class="sign_in block">
  <%= link_to signin_path('github'), class: "button" do %>
    <%= image_tag("github.png", width: "32") %>
    Sign in with GitHub
  <% end %>
  or
  <%= link_to signin_path('twitter'), class: "button" do %>
    <%= image_tag("twitter.png", width: "32") %>
    Sign in with Twitter
  <% end %>
  <p>Sign in to start tracking your pomodoros.</p>
</div>